WEBVTT

00:01.234 --> 00:04.185
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.220 --> 00:06.454
Hey, Cliffy.
Oh, hey, Sam.

00:06.455 --> 00:08.122
What are you doing
standing out in the rain?

00:08.124 --> 00:09.257
Uh, it's good for the skin.

00:09.258 --> 00:11.410
You know, negative ions.
Keeps it soft.

00:11.444 --> 00:13.578
What'd you say
to Carla, Cliffy.

00:13.612 --> 00:15.313
Called her a dwarf.

00:15.315 --> 00:16.681
Oh.

00:16.682 --> 00:17.982
Could you, uh, untie me, Sam?

00:17.983 --> 00:19.451
Yeah, sure.

00:19.452 --> 00:21.603
Thanks. Oh, whoa, whoa, wait
a second, wait a second.

00:21.604 --> 00:23.171
How much more time
you got out here?

00:23.172 --> 00:24.856
Uh, five minutes.

00:24.891 --> 00:26.508
I'm sorry, buddy,
I can't do it.

00:26.509 --> 00:28.510
She'd have me standing
right out here next to you.

00:28.511 --> 00:29.578
I understand, Sam,
I understand.

00:29.579 --> 00:30.579
No hard feelings.

00:30.580 --> 00:31.713
(theme song begins)

